{"tid":1454543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組請入。","createTime":"2019-08-12T07:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T07:47:39.000Z","uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d38320790d8ca0065aadb9d0b0cb3d4b651035ae","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"張國榮有首歌叫最冷一天。啲歌詞好配合昨晚嘅感嘅  可以配圖做mv  我唔識整只能提供意見"},{"pid":"adaf51670913c87270b2c92b381dda69e48a946a","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:45:58.000Z","msg":"最冷一天<br />\n如果傷感比快樂更深<br />\n但願我一樣伴你行<br />\n當抬頭迎面總有密雲<br />\n只要認得你再沒有遺憾<br />\n如果苦笑比眼淚更真<br />\n但願笑聲像一滴滴吻<br />\n如明日好景忽遠忽近<br />\n仍願抱著這份情沒疑問<br />\n任面前時代再低氣溫<br />\n多麼的慶幸 長夜無需一個人<br />\n任未來存在哪個可能<br />\n和你亦是 最後那對變更<br />\n唯願在剩餘光線面前<br />\n留下兩眼為見你一面<br />\n仍然能相擁才不怕驟變 但怕思念<br />\n唯願會及時擁抱入眠<br />\n留住這世上最暖一面<br />\n茫茫人海取暖渡過 最冷一天"},{"pid":"147d8359493528af76a923c412e07e8f615599f2","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6a637a890505e1d49eb91413013b550e2889bcfe","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:46:45.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"504d404adfe8d51548bb0fa822f315fcd259c1bb","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d47cf9964e0bf1f5fb75dbfa817b79b6fe63d176","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:47:05.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9d42ee88df2abe80b24079431085e5891c203858","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:47:22.000Z","msg":"留下兩眼為見你一面"},{"pid":"4259ee81e9b2ea3bec14e610a699543254d9492f","tid":1454543,"uid":156275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"留下兩眼為見你一面"}]}